articles.author: Lindsy Neer, Ryan Autullo and Tony Plohetski, Austin American-Statesman
articles.title: What we know about Anna Wilson's death: Who is Kaitlin Armstrong? - Austin American-Statesman
articles.description: Kaitlin Armstrong is accused of killing Anna Wilson, a cyclist who was shot in Austin. Police say Wilson previously dated Armstrong's boyfriend.
articles.content: An Austin woman is accused by police of killing professional cyclist Anna Moriah Wilson. An arrest warrant affidavit includes allegations of a possible love triangle among Wilson, another professiona… [+3038 chars]
